author_ssm: Matt Moore, 2001. Edited by Rhyannon J. Rodriguez 2012, 2014, and 2015.
abstract_ssm: The Margaret Strickland Papers feature the original typescripts of the English writer's biographical works, novels, plays, short stories, and short non-fiction pieces. In addition, this collection includes correspondence, diaries, hand-assembled illustrated magazines, photographs, and scrapbooks, dating from the 1880s to early 1960s.
